Read TSO TMB_Trace File

Source: R/tso.R
tso_tmbt_read.Rd

Reads the TMB_Trace.tsv file output from the TSO500 workflow.

Usage

tso_tmbt_read(x)

Arguments

x

Path to file.

Examples

x <- system.file("extdata/tso/sample705_TMB_Trace.tsv", package = "dracarys")
tso_tmbt_read(x)
